==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: hot-wire
<hw>hot-wire</hw> <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>to start (a car) by using a wire
instead of a key, as when stealing the car; the wire is connected to
points in the ignition circuit that bypass the key.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

